 Securities Exchange Act of 1934 is recorded, processed, summarized and reported, within", "bbox": [162.5, 820.6, 1112.5, 841.4]}, {"text": "the time periods specified in the Securities and Exchange Commission’s rules and forms. These disclosure", "bbox": [162.5, 845.6, 1112.3, 866.4]}, {"text": "controls and procedures include controls and procedures designed to ensure that information required to be", "bbox": [162.5, 870.6, 1112.5, 891.4]}, {"text": "disclosed under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 is accumulated and communicated to the company’s", "bbox": [162.5, 895.6, 1112.3, 916.4]}, {"text": "management on a timely basis to allow decisions regarding required disclosure. The company evaluated the", "bbox": [162.5, 920.6, 1112.5, 941.4]}, {"text": "effectiveness of the design and operation of its disclosure controls and procedures as of December 31, 2003.", "bbox": [162.5, 945.6, 1112.5, 966.4]}, {"text": "Based on this evaluation, the company’s Chief Executive Officer and Chief Financial Officer have concluded", "bbox": [162.5, 970.6, 1112.4, 991.4]}, {"text": "that as of December 31, 2003, these controls and procedures were effective.", "bbox": [162.5, 995.6, 795.1, 1016.4]}, {"text": "(b) Change in Internal Controls. There have been no changes in internal controls over financial reporting", "bbox": [162.5, 1045.6, 1112.3, 1066.4]}, {"text": "identified in connection with the foregoing evaluation that occurred during the company’s last fiscal quarter that", "bbox": [162.5, 1070.6, 1112.4, 1091.4]}, {"text": "has materially affected, or is reasonably likely to materially affect, the company’s internal control over financial", "bbox": [162.5, 1095.6, 1112.3, 1116.4]}, {"text": "reporting.", "bbox": [162.5, 1120.6, 244.0, 1141.4]}, {"text": "109", "bbox": [621.9, 1483.1, 653.1, 1503.9]}]}